manifest_description.message: The simplest and most effective way to locate a malicious or faulty extension.

ui_info.message: This extension is used to assist in locating malicious or faulty extensions. After you start your search, the following steps are performed:

ui_info_step2.message: Ask if the extension you are looking for is still running and further narrow your search based on the results.

ui_info_step3.message: Cycle steps 1 and 2 until there is only one extension.

notification_zero.message: The number of searchable extensions is zero.

notification_confirm.message: Please manually test whether the extension you are searching for is still running. Select the corresponding option based on the result.
